Insurance Bot ü§ñüìÑ

A Telegram bot for creating and registering car insurance policies. The bot extracts data from passport and vehicle registration documents and generates an insurance policy using AI.

Features

üì∏ Passport data recognition from photos

üöó Vehicle registration certificate recognition (2 pages)

‚úçÔ∏è Manual data input support

üìù Insurance policy generation using Groq AI

üì§ Delivery of the generated policy as a text file

Technologies

Python 3.10+

python-telegram-bot (v20.3)

Mindee API (document recognition)

Groq API (AI text generation)

python-dotenv (environment configuration)

Installation & Run

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt


Create a .env file with your API keys:

TELEGRAM_TOKEN=""
MINDEE_API_KEY=""
GROQ_API_KEY=""


Update Mindee POST and GET requests and adjust data field names according to your document models.

Run the bot:

python main.py

